<anchor id="wakeup__cnt_8h_1wakeup_cnt"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The wakeup counter counts the number of </para>
</simplesect>
<xrefsect id="todo_1_todo000018"><xreftitle>Todo</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>boot events. The boot counter willl be stored persistently in FRAM flash file system. At startup boot count is read from flash file system and will be incremented by 1. Because boot count may be negative on an erased flash it is set to 0 in case of a negative value.</para>
</xrefdescription></xrefsect></para>
